Name: Campfire - Complete Camping System (Supports Skyrim VR)
Description: Campfire is the most feature-rich stand-alone camping mod for The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim, created from Frostfall's immersive and detailed camping system. Campfire is also a modder's framework, allowing anyone to create their own unique camping equipment.
Author: Chesko

Name: Chanterelle - a savage world to explore
Description: A world made to be used with Campfire/Hunterborn. Huge, no civilization. Can be used to expand the Falkreath forest, four portal between Chanterelle and Falkreath hold. Some merchants specialized in hunt products to help you stay longer here.
Author: Vactrol

Name: Fores New Idles in Skyrim SE - FNIS SE
Description: No custom animation possible for Skyrim? Wrong. FNIS Behaviors allows to add different types of animations to the game: idles/poses, sequenced, furniture, paired, killmoves, creatures, and others.
Author: fore

Name: Immersive Sounds - Compendium
Description: A dramatic and extensively customizable overhaul of Skyrim's sound.
Author: lazygecko

Name: Improved Weapon Impact EFFECTS Correct Metal SE - Immersive Sounds Patch
Description: Simple patch to bring the sparks to the newly-added sounds for 2HWeapons in Immersive Sounds, making those weapon types use the improved effects together with the new sounds.
FileName: Improved Weapon Impact EFFECTS Correct Metal SE - Immersive Sounds Patch-38686-1-0-1595773353.rar
Author: Mur4s4me - Lordaloa - Mafjora - lazyskeever

Name: Boethiah for Good Guys
Description: Complete Boethiah's quest without betraying a friend.
Author: Iceburg

Name: Namira for Good Guys
Description: Play a trick on Namira! Complete Namira's quest "The Taste of Death" without sacrificing a priest to Cannibals.
Author: Iceburg

Name: Improved Weapon Impact EFFECTS Correct Metal SE
Description: A cleaned with SSEEdit version of an Oldrim mod with the same name by Lordaloa.
